# UI Architecture & Design System

- **Framework**: Next.js (App Router).
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4.
- **Animations**: Framer Motion (use `motion.div` with scroll-driven entry animations).
- **Theming**: Must support both light and dark mode via `next-themes`. 
  - Do NOT use generic colors. Dark mode uses deep space purples/blues (`bg-card`, `border-white/10`). 
  - Primary accent color is neon cyan (`#00ffe7`).
- **Component Rules**: Do NOT pull in heavy third-party UI component libraries if not absolutely necessary. Stick to bespoke, customized components to maintain the "AI Native / Cyberpunk" aesthetic.
